description:
I love this place! I sometimes come and get a coffee and a pastry on an early weekend morning and read the news on my phone while staring in amazement at the giant woman in the back baking all that goodness. It's one of my weird little rituals. 

For lunch there are $2 piroshkis that are not only delicious but a decent size. yay!!

try this spot. It's so reasonable and so delicious. Plus super authentic :)
